    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Crude Weapon Specialists.</strong></em> Myneyrshi are used to making do with less. You can spend 1 hour, which you can do over the course of a short rest, crafting a weapon out of loose materials. You can craft any simple kinetic weapon, but the weapon’s damage suffers a -1 penalty.</p>",
